  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/2d1c9581c53a3bb0e2b6bc23f254301b.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=506 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/2d1c9581c53a3bb0e2b6bc23f254301b.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/2d1c9581c53a3bb0e2b6bc23f254301b.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Milord is a Kingdom Management RPG game with city building mechanics. Will your subjects die or rise? You decide! You'll have to make hard decisions as the ruler of your fiefdom. You also need to preserve your limited resources. You'll get to choose how you'll remembered; as a charismatic leader or a tyrant is all up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/d5840b6c3930eec85b1f59079d806771.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=530 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/d5840b6c3930eec85b1f59079d806771.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/d5840b6c3930eec85b1f59079d806771.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For Valor and Glory!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into the different stories with the petitioning system where you have your subjects asking for your help. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the rich storyline with full of backstabbing, war and tough choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make allies or conquer them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many ways to end the war. However you must prepare yourself for the consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/36e17f3e3003bf9211ce42e87e29a2f3.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/36e17f3e3003bf9211ce42e87e29a2f3.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/36e17f3e3003bf9211ce42e87e29a2f3.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Capital</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stable kingdom needs a stable economy. With different type of buildings you can improve your fiefdom help you reclaim the destined lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/c0e08cd2bd0a9f388d1ca6ef86e11150.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=462 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/c0e08cd2bd0a9f388d1ca6ef86e11150.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/c0e08cd2bd0a9f388d1ca6ef86e11150.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Land is yours milord!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can move your army and battle against your enemies!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/2d1c9581c53a3bb0e2b6bc23f254301b.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=506 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/2d1c9581c53a3bb0e2b6bc23f254301b.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/2d1c9581c53a3bb0e2b6bc23f254301b.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Milord is a Kingdom Management RPG game with city building mechanics. Will your subjects die or rise? You decide! You'll have to make hard decisions as the ruler of your fiefdom. You also need to preserve your limited resources. You'll get to choose how you'll remembered; as a charismatic leader or a tyrant is all up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/d5840b6c3930eec85b1f59079d806771.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=530 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/d5840b6c3930eec85b1f59079d806771.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/d5840b6c3930eec85b1f59079d806771.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For Valor and Glory!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into the different stories with the petitioning system where you have your subjects asking for your help. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the rich storyline with full of backstabbing, war and tough choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make allies or conquer them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many ways to end the war. However you must prepare yourself for the consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/36e17f3e3003bf9211ce42e87e29a2f3.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/36e17f3e3003bf9211ce42e87e29a2f3.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/36e17f3e3003bf9211ce42e87e29a2f3.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Capital</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stable kingdom needs a stable economy. With different type of buildings you can improve your fiefdom help you reclaim the destined lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/c0e08cd2bd0a9f388d1ca6ef86e11150.poster.avif?t=1765107067\" width=462 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/c0e08cd2bd0a9f388d1ca6ef86e11150.webm?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455460/extras/c0e08cd2bd0a9f388d1ca6ef86e11150.mp4?t=1765107067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Land is yours milord!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can move your army and battle against your enemies!</p>",
